WEBVTT

01:30.830 --> 01:34.979
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:36.070 --> 01:39.520
[2010]

01:36.840 --> 01:38.039
Feel free to look around here.

01:38.039 --> 01:39.840
Let me know if you need anything.

01:42.759 --> 01:43.280
Hello.

01:43.479 --> 01:44.310
Is there any layout

01:44.310 --> 01:45.570
you are interested in?

01:45.680 --> 01:46.229
Hello.

01:46.560 --> 01:47.509
I'd like to ask,

01:47.590 --> 01:49.229
how much is the smallest unit here?

01:49.229 --> 01:50.120
Here's our floor plan.

01:50.120 --> 01:51.150
Please take a look.

01:51.150 --> 01:54.210
The down payment for the smallest unit
is 800,000 yuan.

01:55.590 --> 01:55.950
Okay.

01:55.970 --> 01:57.070
Take a look first.

01:57.070 --> 01:58.870
Let me know if you need anything.

01:59.310 --> 01:59.920
Hello.

01:59.950 --> 02:01.090
Any layout you're interested in?

02:01.090 --> 02:02.150
You can take a look.

02:02.560 --> 02:03.690
Come on, take a look.

02:04.010 --> 02:05.680
These are three-bedroom,
two-living-room units.

02:05.680 --> 02:06.790
The layouts are excellent,

02:06.790 --> 02:08.150
with great north-south ventilation.

02:08.150 --> 02:09.590
We've got very well-developed

02:09.590 --> 02:11.790
surrounding facilities and greenery.

02:11.920 --> 02:13.190
The units on that side
have already sold out.

02:13.190 --> 02:14.590
Only this section is still available now.

02:14.590 --> 02:15.000
Yes.

02:15.120 --> 02:16.680
It's a very popular layout.

02:15.470 --> 02:18.360
[Episode 12]
[Don't Look Down on the Poor Youth]

02:19.800 --> 02:20.530
Here you are.

02:20.560 --> 02:21.360
Okay, thanks.

02:26.310 --> 02:27.560
Did the call get through?

02:27.560 --> 02:28.420
It got through,

02:28.630 --> 02:29.840
but the subdistrict office said

02:29.840 --> 02:31.840
they can't reach her family either.

02:32.030 --> 02:32.910
I figured.

02:33.630 --> 02:36.079
The rental agent mentioned before

02:36.430 --> 02:38.160
that Granny Yu only has one son,

02:38.290 --> 02:39.400
who took his wife and child

02:39.400 --> 02:40.560
abroad

02:40.590 --> 02:41.590
over 20 years ago.

02:41.840 --> 02:43.600
There hasn't been any news of them since.

02:43.600 --> 02:45.000
Granny Yu just stayed in the house,

02:45.000 --> 02:46.560
waiting for him to come back.

02:46.560 --> 02:47.590
Granny Yu used to be

02:47.590 --> 02:49.470
a young lady from a prominent family.

02:49.470 --> 02:50.870
She's quite stubborn.

02:50.960 --> 02:52.400
I guess she took her medicine

02:52.400 --> 02:53.960
and got injections in secret,

02:53.960 --> 02:54.710
not wanting us to see

02:54.710 --> 02:55.910
her vulnerable side.

03:01.430 --> 03:01.960
Let's go.

03:22.079 --> 03:22.880
You're awake.

03:23.079 --> 03:23.940
How do you feel?

03:24.050 --> 03:24.750
I'll call the doctor.

03:24.750 --> 03:25.840
I want dim sum.

03:27.280 --> 03:27.800
Okay.

03:28.430 --> 03:29.360
I'll go buy some.

03:36.400 --> 03:36.910
Granny.

03:37.120 --> 03:38.310
That's your granddaughter, right?

03:38.310 --> 03:40.650
She sent her mom home to sleep last night

03:40.680 --> 03:42.660
and stayed by your side all night herself.

03:42.660 --> 03:43.660
That young lady

03:43.800 --> 03:45.240
is both pretty and filial.

03:45.240 --> 03:46.300
You're so blessed.

03:47.079 --> 03:48.680
She's not my granddaughter.

03:50.040 --> 03:51.370
Can Granny Yu really eat

03:51.470 --> 03:53.000
these pastries you bought?

03:53.040 --> 03:54.590
Since Granny Yu specifically
asked for them,

03:54.590 --> 03:55.990
I have to buy them anyway.

03:56.000 --> 03:57.530
Don't worry. I've got a way.

03:59.310 --> 04:00.240
Comrade Liu Fen.

04:00.530 --> 04:01.260
Xia Xiaolan.

04:02.120 --> 04:02.910
Mr. Tang.

04:03.710 --> 04:04.840
What a coincidence—

04:05.120 --> 04:06.150
to run into each other

04:06.150 --> 04:07.610
in a place like a hospital.

04:08.080 --> 04:08.740
Mayor Tang,

04:09.240 --> 04:10.150
I'll go get the car.

04:10.150 --> 04:10.840
Please wait a moment.

04:10.840 --> 04:11.170
Okay.

04:13.840 --> 04:15.900
Mr. Tang, are you here for a check-up?

04:16.480 --> 04:17.390
It's nothing serious.

04:17.390 --> 04:18.790
Thanks for your concern.

04:19.480 --> 04:20.630
What's going on with you two?

04:20.630 --> 04:21.959
Who's not feeling well?

04:22.120 --> 04:22.870
It's not us.

04:22.870 --> 04:24.690
Our landlord is in the hospital,

04:24.950 --> 04:26.950
so we went to buy her some breakfast.

04:27.040 --> 04:28.390
You guys are truly kind-hearted.

04:28.390 --> 04:29.430
You always lend a hand to

04:29.430 --> 04:30.630
anyone who's in trouble.

04:30.630 --> 04:32.360
I really should learn from you.

04:33.950 --> 04:34.560
Mr. Tang,

04:34.810 --> 04:35.950
since there's nothing else,

04:35.950 --> 04:37.070
we'll head up now.

04:37.120 --> 04:38.680
We still need to deliver breakfast
to Granny Yu.

04:38.680 --> 04:39.270
Alright.

04:39.720 --> 04:40.980
Oh right, Xia Xiaolan.

04:41.360 --> 04:42.170
I remember

04:42.240 --> 04:43.000
you were planning to open

04:43.000 --> 04:44.070
a clothing store, right?

04:44.070 --> 04:44.510
Yes.

04:45.000 --> 04:46.000
Has it opened yet?

04:46.190 --> 04:47.430
We're still preparing.

04:47.430 --> 04:48.830
We don't want to just open

04:48.830 --> 04:49.870
a run-of-the-mill little shop.

04:49.870 --> 04:51.670
We're aiming to open a boutique.

04:52.190 --> 04:53.750
Well, you really are
quite forward-thinking.

04:53.750 --> 04:54.870
Shengcheng

04:54.950 --> 04:56.070
is developing

04:56.070 --> 04:57.070
very rapidly right now.

04:57.070 --> 04:58.070
It definitely needs

04:58.070 --> 04:59.750
some high-quality boutiques.

04:59.750 --> 05:00.950
If you encounter any difficulties,

05:00.950 --> 05:02.610
have your mother come find me.

05:04.800 --> 05:06.070
Well, we'll head up then.

05:06.070 --> 05:06.400
Okay.

05:06.630 --> 05:06.890
Okay.

05:06.890 --> 05:07.430
Thank you, Mr. Tang.

05:07.430 --> 05:07.960
Goodbye.

05:08.070 --> 05:08.600
Goodbye.

05:12.120 --> 05:12.650
Goodbye.

05:12.830 --> 05:13.360
Goodbye.

05:14.240 --> 05:14.600
Mom.

05:15.230 --> 05:17.030
Since when did you and Mayor Tang

05:17.030 --> 05:17.960
become so close?

05:18.190 --> 05:21.320
He even said things like
"have your mother come find me"?

05:21.800 --> 05:22.680
Well, your auntie

05:22.680 --> 05:23.310
sent us a lot of

05:23.310 --> 05:24.830
specialties from Yunan, right?

05:24.830 --> 05:26.560
I knew he used to work in Yunan,

05:26.720 --> 05:27.720
so I gave him some.

05:28.870 --> 05:29.400
Xiaolan,

05:29.720 --> 05:31.630
are you able to rent that shop?

05:32.310 --> 05:33.970
I haven't found the owner yet.

05:34.240 --> 05:35.770
I'll figure something out.

05:37.800 --> 05:39.159
Shrimp dumplings,

05:40.600 --> 05:42.920
red bean cake with orange peel,

05:43.240 --> 05:44.630
barbecue pork buns,

05:45.240 --> 05:46.950
and Shumai.

05:48.630 --> 05:49.310
Granny Yu,

05:49.630 --> 05:51.480
I bought all this dim sum

05:51.480 --> 05:53.090
from Lan Kwai Restaurant for you.

05:53.090 --> 05:53.840
The doctor says

05:53.840 --> 05:55.630
you need protein right now.

05:56.159 --> 05:57.800
As for these high-sugar treats,

05:57.800 --> 05:58.750
you can eat them,

05:59.040 --> 05:59.920
but if you do,

05:59.920 --> 06:02.240
you'll have to stay in the hospital
longer.

06:02.240 --> 06:03.980
The choice is yours.

06:04.190 --> 06:05.360
Will you eat these,

06:05.630 --> 06:06.720
or these?

06:07.130 --> 06:08.570
These eggs and soy milk

06:08.600 --> 06:10.530
are also from Lan Kwai Restaurant.

06:19.480 --> 06:20.510
L-Let me help you.

06:20.630 --> 06:21.760
I'll peel it for you.

06:23.720 --> 06:25.720
Your daughter is really something—

06:26.390 --> 06:27.980
so young,

06:28.190 --> 06:30.980
yet she has so many thoughtful ways
of taking care of people.

06:30.980 --> 06:33.310
Granny Yu, I'll take that as a compliment.

06:34.480 --> 06:35.310
Don't waste these.

06:35.310 --> 06:36.110
I'll eat them.

06:36.120 --> 06:37.480
I'll finish these.

06:41.310 --> 06:41.720
Here.

06:42.720 --> 06:44.050
It's really delicious.

06:44.510 --> 06:45.190
Granny Yu.

06:45.310 --> 06:46.270
Lan Kwai Restaurant is really nice.

06:46.270 --> 06:47.480
You really have great taste.

06:47.480 --> 06:48.270
Is it that good?

06:48.270 --> 06:49.120
Have a taste. Here.

06:49.120 --> 06:49.450
Okay.

06:52.000 --> 06:52.950
It's good, right?

06:52.950 --> 06:54.280
It's really delicious.

06:54.510 --> 06:58.840
♪ Along the long road ahead,
how much beauty awaits ♪

06:58.870 --> 07:02.460
♪ I'll take time to appreciate it all ♪

07:03.320 --> 07:07.220
♪ Why pause and look back? ♪

07:07.790 --> 07:11.060
♪ My heart feels so confused ♪

07:08.270 --> 07:09.040
You're here.

07:09.240 --> 07:09.600
Let me tell you,

07:09.600 --> 07:10.720
there's so much work to do.

07:10.720 --> 07:11.680
Sis Bai and I have been so busy

07:11.650 --> 07:15.520
♪ Silently, I watch the clouds
drift in the sky ♪

07:11.680 --> 07:12.480
that we haven't even had a bite to eat.

07:12.480 --> 07:13.510
You're certainly enthusiastic.

07:13.510 --> 07:14.720
But aren't you supposed to be
taking care of your own shop?

07:14.720 --> 07:16.190
Sis Bai's junior is watching it.

07:15.270 --> 07:17.330
[Zhenzhu Building Materials Shop]

07:16.190 --> 07:20.640
♪ Just like you and I,
our ambitions reach far and wide ♪

07:16.630 --> 07:17.160
Sis Bai.

07:17.190 --> 07:18.240
Come on. They're here.

07:18.240 --> 07:19.000
Xiaolan!

07:19.720 --> 07:20.680
Xiaolan!

07:20.660 --> 07:24.620
♪ I hope to wander joyfully with you ♪

07:20.680 --> 07:22.120
I finally opened my own shop!

07:22.120 --> 07:23.430
I'm so happy!

07:24.480 --> 07:25.010
Zhenzhu.

07:25.240 --> 07:25.830
Congratulations.

07:25.280 --> 07:29.840
♪ Hand in hand, exploring strange lands ♪

07:26.040 --> 07:26.800
Thank you.

07:29.360 --> 07:29.890
And this.

07:30.160 --> 07:30.800
What's this?

07:30.350 --> 07:34.470
♪ The road ahead is full of storms ♪

07:31.480 --> 07:32.510
Xiaolan thought for a long time

07:32.510 --> 07:33.560
about what gift to get you.

07:33.560 --> 07:35.070
She decided to give you a landline.

07:35.000 --> 07:38.380
♪ I'll get by them one by one ♪

07:35.270 --> 07:37.330
Someone will come to install it soon.

07:37.360 --> 07:38.920
That's a big gift.

07:39.190 --> 07:40.630
Oh my god.

07:39.370 --> 07:43.380
♪ We'll guard each other
on the road ahead ♪

07:40.830 --> 07:42.480
This is too expensive.

07:42.510 --> 07:43.870
In all of Renmin Bridge,

07:43.870 --> 07:45.159
few people have landlines.

07:44.400 --> 07:47.170
♪ Don't be afraid of the long path ♪

07:45.270 --> 07:46.070
I have a pager,

07:46.070 --> 07:47.270
which is already very convenient.

07:47.270 --> 07:48.159
Isn't that perfect?

07:47.800 --> 07:51.510
♪ With you,
there won't be despair on this path ♪

07:48.510 --> 07:49.480
Zhenzhu Building Materials

07:49.480 --> 07:51.310
is leading the way in Renmin Bridge again.

07:51.310 --> 07:52.870
With a landline, it's easier
to stay in touch.

07:52.180 --> 07:56.480
♪ With you, my faith grows stronger ♪

07:52.950 --> 07:54.040
And it can even bring in some income.

07:54.040 --> 07:55.700
If anyone wants to make a call,

07:55.720 --> 07:57.850
you can charge them 2 dimes per minute.

07:58.560 --> 07:59.270
Xiaolan.

07:59.270 --> 08:00.630
Why are you so smart?

08:00.950 --> 08:01.810
I'll accept it.

08:02.190 --> 08:03.750
You've been renting the shop

08:03.750 --> 08:04.600
and stocking up recently.

08:04.600 --> 08:05.240
If there's anything

08:05.240 --> 08:06.060
you need help with,

08:06.060 --> 08:06.990
just let me know.

08:07.360 --> 08:07.760
Right.

08:07.870 --> 08:08.430
You can tell us too.

08:08.430 --> 08:09.390
We also made some money

08:09.390 --> 08:10.480
from our business before.

08:10.480 --> 08:11.800
Don't hesitate.

08:12.310 --> 08:13.920
I won't hesitate.

08:13.920 --> 08:15.160
You can't imagine how happy I am.

08:15.160 --> 08:16.120
Come on. Come on in.

08:16.120 --> 08:17.270
Let me show you around.

08:17.270 --> 08:17.870
Over here,

08:17.870 --> 08:19.680
I plan to display lighting fixtures.

08:19.680 --> 08:20.340
Here, here.

08:20.430 --> 08:21.290
Come over here.

08:22.600 --> 08:23.730
I'll put paint here,

08:23.750 --> 08:24.720
tiles there,

08:24.720 --> 08:26.600
and some small furniture in the middle.

08:26.600 --> 08:27.600
What do you think?

08:28.310 --> 08:29.000
Zhenzhu.

08:29.190 --> 08:30.870
Your shop isn't very big.

08:31.070 --> 08:33.070
You'd better focus on one category,

08:33.270 --> 08:34.270
something distinctive

08:34.270 --> 08:35.240
that sets your shop apart

08:35.240 --> 08:36.240
from other shops.

08:36.480 --> 08:37.409
One category...

08:38.789 --> 08:40.390
How about lighting fixtures?

08:40.390 --> 08:41.320
There are so many types

08:41.320 --> 08:42.720
of lighting fixtures nowadays.

08:42.720 --> 08:43.840
Before, to buy a lamp,

08:43.840 --> 08:44.750
you had to go to Longcheng

08:44.750 --> 08:45.550
or Jingcheng.

08:45.910 --> 08:46.870
Lighting fixtures will be
my shop's specialty,

08:46.870 --> 08:48.840
but I want to sell other products too.

08:48.840 --> 08:50.150
After all, when people come all the way
to Renmin Bridge,

08:50.150 --> 08:51.030
they'd want to

08:51.030 --> 08:51.600
bring more things home,

08:51.600 --> 08:52.030
right?

08:55.150 --> 08:55.680
Xiaolan.

08:56.320 --> 08:57.750
When Zhenzhu asked you just now,

08:57.750 --> 08:58.690
you'd already decided to suggest

08:58.690 --> 09:00.030
she focus on selling lighting fixtures,
right?

09:00.030 --> 09:01.630
Why didn't you just tell her?

09:02.150 --> 09:03.720
If I told her everything,

09:03.870 --> 09:05.270
she would just rely on me.

09:05.360 --> 09:06.930
Sis Bai is actually very smart.

09:06.930 --> 09:08.240
She catches on quickly.

09:08.240 --> 09:09.000
In business,

09:09.150 --> 09:10.750
you have to rely on yourself.

09:12.270 --> 09:12.960
Boss,

09:13.350 --> 09:15.530
two orders of barbecue pork rice

09:15.670 --> 09:17.120
and one order of pig trotter rice, please.

09:17.120 --> 09:17.600
Okay.

09:18.480 --> 09:20.150
Not giving direct advice

09:20.790 --> 09:22.030
was both to let Bai Zhenzhu

09:22.030 --> 09:23.230
think independently

09:23.630 --> 09:24.960
and because I'm afraid—

09:25.570 --> 09:26.720
afraid that getting too involved in

09:26.720 --> 09:27.850
someone else's life

09:28.200 --> 09:30.460
could lead to unexpected consequences.

09:31.860 --> 09:33.080
There are quite a few dietary restrictions

09:33.080 --> 09:33.960
for diabetics.

09:34.150 --> 09:35.750
So what can and can't she eat?

09:35.750 --> 09:36.890
Could you tell me again?

09:36.890 --> 09:37.550
I've already written it down.

09:37.550 --> 09:38.480
Just take a look.

09:39.000 --> 09:40.120
Okay, thank you.

09:40.850 --> 09:41.780
Granny Yu.

09:41.920 --> 09:43.090
Don't argue with me.

09:43.120 --> 09:44.720
Just have a good rest for now.

09:50.170 --> 09:50.930
Pay the fees

09:50.960 --> 09:52.120
and she can be discharged.

09:52.120 --> 09:52.910
Okay, thanks.

09:52.910 --> 09:53.720
Thanks, Doctor.

09:53.720 --> 09:54.440
I'll pay.

09:55.480 --> 09:55.880
You...

09:57.840 --> 09:59.240
What a stubborn old lady.

09:59.960 --> 10:00.690
Give it to me.

10:15.870 --> 10:16.670
How is it?

10:16.690 --> 10:19.950
We've kept the courtyard
in pretty good shape, haven't we?

10:23.030 --> 10:24.160
Where are you going?

10:24.630 --> 10:26.390
I haven't swept the streets in days.

10:26.390 --> 10:28.590
I'll go notify the subdistrict office.

10:28.750 --> 10:29.870
Don't worry about it.

10:29.870 --> 10:31.160
You just got out of the hospital.

10:31.160 --> 10:33.000
I already spoke to the subdistrict office

10:33.000 --> 10:33.960
about your hospitalization

10:33.960 --> 10:35.400
and had them hire a substitute.

10:35.400 --> 10:36.240
But don't worry—

10:36.240 --> 10:37.550
I specifically told them

10:37.550 --> 10:39.480
the substitute is temporary.

10:39.720 --> 10:42.780
The job is still yours
now that you've been discharged.

10:44.790 --> 10:47.640
Five dimes a day...

10:48.440 --> 10:49.600
Two days...

10:49.600 --> 10:51.330
What is Granny Yu calculating?

10:52.030 --> 10:53.360
She's calculating how much pay she missed

10:53.360 --> 10:55.160
during her days in the hospital.

10:55.200 --> 10:55.960
She just got discharged

10:55.960 --> 10:57.510
and can't start working immediately.

10:57.510 --> 11:00.510
She has to factor in the losses
for the days ahead, too.

11:01.240 --> 11:02.960
Go tell the subdistrict office

11:02.960 --> 11:04.290
to fire the substitute.

11:04.910 --> 11:06.870
I'll sweep the streets myself tomorrow.

11:06.870 --> 11:07.440
Okay.

11:20.790 --> 11:22.750
My... My broom...

11:23.150 --> 11:24.960
Good morning, Granny Yu.

11:25.910 --> 11:27.770
Did you take your medicine today?

11:29.510 --> 11:31.720
That's no way to greet someone.

11:32.540 --> 11:33.540
Give me the broom.

11:34.120 --> 11:35.550
I've already finished sweeping for you.

11:35.550 --> 11:36.790
I made millet porridge this morning.

11:36.790 --> 11:37.850
I'll get you a bowl.

11:38.150 --> 11:39.550
Get me a bowl of millet porridge too.

11:39.550 --> 11:40.000
Yong.

11:41.000 --> 11:42.000
Hello, Granny Yu.

11:42.120 --> 11:42.480
Yong.

11:43.670 --> 11:44.840
How's it going with the shop?

11:44.840 --> 11:45.720
Were you able to rent it?

11:45.720 --> 11:47.440
That's what I came to talk to you about.

11:47.440 --> 11:48.130
It can only be rented

11:48.130 --> 11:49.480
if the other owner of that shop

11:49.480 --> 11:51.150
on 27th Road agrees.

11:51.840 --> 11:53.050
I'm planning to go with Xiaolan

11:53.050 --> 11:54.170
and Chen Xiliang

11:54.200 --> 11:55.450
to discuss it again

11:55.480 --> 11:56.200
with Mr. Yuan,

11:56.200 --> 11:57.320
to show our sincerity

11:57.320 --> 11:58.000
and see if he can

11:58.000 --> 11:59.750
give us that person's information.

11:59.750 --> 12:00.150
Okay.

12:00.270 --> 12:00.720
Alright.

12:00.720 --> 12:01.390
Come have breakfast then.

12:01.390 --> 12:01.920
Hurry up.

12:02.100 --> 12:02.810
Granny Yu.

12:02.840 --> 12:04.570
I'll bring it in for you in a bit.

12:11.150 --> 12:11.870
Guys.

12:12.200 --> 12:13.960
I can feel

12:14.150 --> 12:15.390
your sincerity.

12:15.670 --> 12:16.720
But as I said,

12:17.380 --> 12:19.290
since the other owner of this shop

12:19.310 --> 12:20.000
disagrees,

12:20.120 --> 12:21.720
I can't rent it to you.

12:22.480 --> 12:23.000
Mr. Yuan.

12:23.000 --> 12:23.630
Please help us

12:23.630 --> 12:24.760
contact them again.

12:25.360 --> 12:27.270
If it's really too difficult for you,

12:27.270 --> 12:28.670
just give their address and phone number

12:28.670 --> 12:29.150
to us.

12:29.150 --> 12:30.030
We'll contact them ourselves.

12:30.030 --> 12:30.600
Okay?

12:30.630 --> 12:31.000
Yeah.

12:31.390 --> 12:33.050
We can go find them ourselves.

12:33.080 --> 12:34.720
If they still disagree in person,

12:34.720 --> 12:36.050
then... Then we'll see.

12:36.600 --> 12:37.840
It's not like there's just

12:37.840 --> 12:39.340
this one vacant shop in Shengcheng.

12:39.340 --> 12:40.750
If you had used this time to look around,

12:40.750 --> 12:41.750
you could have probably rented

12:41.750 --> 12:43.150
another shop.

12:44.030 --> 12:44.840
Mr. Yuan.

12:45.100 --> 12:46.080
What we want to open

12:46.080 --> 12:48.620
is the first branded clothing store
in the country.

12:48.620 --> 12:50.170
We have to rent the best

12:50.200 --> 12:51.600
and most prominent shop.

12:51.870 --> 12:53.000
The one on 27th Road

12:53.030 --> 12:54.240
is truly the best

12:54.240 --> 12:55.030
we can find.

12:55.360 --> 12:55.870
Look.

12:56.240 --> 12:57.910
Isn't this just a dead end?

12:59.360 --> 12:59.910
Come in.

13:04.270 --> 13:04.870
Director,

13:05.550 --> 13:07.080
the property owner is here.

13:07.450 --> 13:08.850
Hurry up and bring her in.

13:11.870 --> 13:12.670
This is weird.

13:12.960 --> 13:14.190
This other owner

13:14.310 --> 13:15.370
came here herself.

13:38.440 --> 13:39.200
Granny Yu?

13:49.240 --> 13:50.030
Granny Yu,

13:50.790 --> 13:52.910
so you are the other owner?

13:55.080 --> 13:56.150
I guess you've

13:56.150 --> 13:58.350
had your eye on that shop for a long time.

13:58.360 --> 13:58.960
That's why

13:58.960 --> 14:00.620
you rented my house, isn't it?

14:01.000 --> 14:01.550
No.

14:01.840 --> 14:02.490
Granny Yu,

14:02.550 --> 14:03.630
I really didn't know

14:03.630 --> 14:05.030
the shop belonged to you.

14:05.200 --> 14:06.200
Now that I know,

14:06.910 --> 14:07.550
I still want

14:07.550 --> 14:08.750
to ask you—

14:09.560 --> 14:10.790
are you willing to rent the shop

14:10.790 --> 14:12.450
to us to open a clothing store?

14:15.930 --> 14:17.320
I think you knew all along

14:17.320 --> 14:18.580
that the shop was mine.

14:19.790 --> 14:20.550
I swear,

14:20.630 --> 14:21.830
I really didn't know.

14:25.390 --> 14:27.670
So you've decided to rent that shop?

14:28.270 --> 14:28.720
Yes.

14:29.360 --> 14:30.270
I must rent it.

14:32.600 --> 14:33.200
Sis Bai.

14:33.630 --> 14:34.870
I'll put them here for you.

14:34.870 --> 14:35.600
Okay.

14:39.750 --> 14:41.150
This calculator is quite expensive.

14:41.150 --> 14:42.550
Be gentle, okay?

14:42.720 --> 14:44.720
If it breaks, we have to buy a new one.

14:44.830 --> 14:45.480
I thought

14:45.510 --> 14:46.910
it would be easier to do business
with acquaintances.

14:46.910 --> 14:48.030
I got ripped off.

14:48.270 --> 14:49.120
Who are you talking about?

14:49.120 --> 14:50.550
That lamp seller from Longcheng?

14:50.550 --> 14:51.270
Yes, him.

14:51.670 --> 14:53.070
I've learned my lesson now.

14:53.070 --> 14:54.390
No matter how close you are,

14:54.390 --> 14:56.720
you must think twice
before making a deal.

14:56.790 --> 14:58.720
A fall into a pit, a gain in your wit.

15:00.600 --> 15:01.270
Granny Yu.

15:01.870 --> 15:03.550
I agree to your conditions.

15:04.150 --> 15:06.150
The rent is 2,000 yuan a year.

15:07.080 --> 15:08.680
Have you thought it through?

15:08.840 --> 15:09.480
Xia,

15:10.000 --> 15:11.840
2,000 yuan is a bit expensive.

15:12.670 --> 15:13.930
Not only will I rent it,

15:13.960 --> 15:16.070
but I will rent it for 10 years.

15:17.670 --> 15:18.510
Ten years?

15:18.910 --> 15:21.440
You want the rent to stay the same
for 10 years?

15:22.150 --> 15:24.410
The rent will increase by 10% every year.

15:24.670 --> 15:26.120
The first year is 2,000 yuan,

15:26.120 --> 15:27.650
the second year 2,200 yuan,

15:27.860 --> 15:28.440
the third year

15:28.440 --> 15:29.840
2,420 yuan.

15:30.190 --> 15:31.550
And by the last year of the lease,

15:31.550 --> 15:32.080
I will pay

15:32.090 --> 15:33.840
4,715.9 yuan.

15:35.240 --> 15:36.100
That's it then.

15:37.510 --> 15:38.080
Deal.

15:39.910 --> 15:41.910
But I have an additional condition.

15:43.200 --> 15:44.150
What condition?

15:46.150 --> 15:48.680
I want the right of first refusal
for the shop.

15:50.200 --> 15:50.790
Xiaolan.

15:51.620 --> 15:53.010
Granny Yu went out this afternoon

15:53.010 --> 15:54.410
and hasn't come back yet.

15:57.240 --> 15:59.440
Granny Yu, you look so beautiful today.

15:59.630 --> 16:01.830
Did you two run into each other just now?

16:02.630 --> 16:04.270
Granny Yu is now our

16:04.270 --> 16:05.440
double landlord.

16:06.660 --> 16:07.750
Don't tell me that shop

16:07.750 --> 16:09.120
belongs to Granny Yu.

16:13.720 --> 16:15.200
All 3 parties were there today,

16:15.200 --> 16:17.460
so we checked the contract and signed it.

16:17.600 --> 16:18.240
Granny Yu.

16:18.550 --> 16:19.270
Thank you.

16:20.750 --> 16:21.750
You should know

16:22.840 --> 16:24.270
the 2,000 yuan annual rent

16:24.270 --> 16:25.600
is what I asked from you.

16:26.630 --> 16:27.960
Why are you thanking me?

16:29.150 --> 16:29.840
Girl,

16:30.360 --> 16:32.030
don't think you're so lucky.

16:32.630 --> 16:33.760
The road ahead of you

16:34.390 --> 16:35.440
is still long.

16:41.190 --> 16:42.790
She doesn't seem very happy.

16:44.270 --> 16:45.400
She probably thinks

16:45.630 --> 16:46.850
I found out somewhere

16:46.880 --> 16:47.930
about the info

16:47.960 --> 16:49.480
of that shop's owner,

16:49.980 --> 16:51.080
and that's why we came

16:51.080 --> 16:52.140
to rent this house—

16:52.440 --> 16:54.370
just to get close to her step by step

16:54.440 --> 16:55.840
in order to get that shop.

16:56.960 --> 16:59.270
She feels her feelings were cheated.

16:59.630 --> 17:00.320
When she asked for the rent,

17:00.320 --> 17:01.980
she didn't go easy on us at all.

17:02.060 --> 17:04.030
We have to explain this clearly to her.

17:04.030 --> 17:05.920
When we rented this house back then,

17:05.920 --> 17:07.550
we just wanted to open a small shop.

17:07.550 --> 17:09.490
We didn't know about that shop at all.

17:09.490 --> 17:11.210
We think it's a coincidence,

17:11.430 --> 17:12.890
but Granny Yu won't buy it.

17:13.069 --> 17:13.920
There hasn't been news of

17:13.920 --> 17:15.520
her own son for over a decade.

17:15.700 --> 17:16.640
How can you expect her to trust

17:16.640 --> 17:19.099
the two of us,
whom she just happened to meet?

17:19.400 --> 17:20.200
But it's okay.

17:20.720 --> 17:23.000
We're renting the shop for 10 years,

17:23.119 --> 17:25.089
and we'll continue living in this house.

17:25.089 --> 17:26.290
We have plenty of time

17:26.349 --> 17:27.810
to warm Granny Yu's heart.

17:32.240 --> 17:32.720
Uncle.

17:33.040 --> 17:33.890
The exterior

17:33.920 --> 17:35.380
doesn't need big changes.

17:35.440 --> 17:36.480
But these spots

17:36.550 --> 17:37.400
must be changed into

17:37.400 --> 17:39.200
this kind of transparent glass
display windows,

17:39.200 --> 17:40.240
so that anyone passing by

17:40.240 --> 17:41.720
can see the new styles inside at a glance.

17:41.720 --> 17:42.120
Got it.

17:42.720 --> 17:44.030
Besides the interior decoration,

17:44.030 --> 17:45.790
we also need a temperature control system

17:45.790 --> 17:47.110
and a special lighting design.

17:45.890 --> 17:49.670
♪ The sunlight fell on me ♪

17:47.400 --> 17:48.880
Do you think that will work?

17:48.880 --> 17:49.510
Xiaolan,

17:49.640 --> 17:50.770
this design of yours

17:50.790 --> 17:53.110
♪ And sets my heart ablaze ♪

17:51.000 --> 17:52.350
is even fancier

17:52.350 --> 17:53.170
than Blue Phoenix in Jingcheng.

17:53.170 --> 17:53.830
I have to go back

17:53.830 --> 17:54.960
and study this carefully.

17:53.890 --> 17:56.190
♪ Are you also the same? ♪

17:55.440 --> 17:57.110
I must ensure we get the effect you want.

17:57.110 --> 17:57.480
Okay.

17:58.030 --> 17:58.510
Uncle.

17:58.890 --> 18:03.090
♪ Dreams will always shine ♪

17:59.030 --> 18:00.920
Zhenzhu is selling building materials now.

18:00.920 --> 18:02.110
If we need anything,

18:02.110 --> 18:02.970
we can tell her.

18:03.200 --> 18:04.590
She'll definitely give us the best.

18:03.990 --> 18:06.500
♪ There may also be regrets ♪

18:04.930 --> 18:06.480
If our renovation turns out well,

18:06.480 --> 18:07.680
it'll be good publicity for her shop too.

18:06.530 --> 18:10.270
♪ If you lose something,
be strong ♪

18:08.030 --> 18:08.480
Okay.

18:08.880 --> 18:10.740
I'll go get the measurements now.

18:10.840 --> 18:13.240
♪ And head to the distant place ♪

18:20.750 --> 18:22.080
Granny Yu, you're back.

18:22.640 --> 18:24.500
Did you take your medicine today?

18:26.480 --> 18:28.400
I did, I did.

18:28.860 --> 18:30.670
Who asks others every day

18:30.700 --> 18:32.300
if they took their medicine?

18:32.640 --> 18:34.970
Look what a sweet talker your daughter is.

18:35.200 --> 18:36.480
You should learn from her.

18:36.480 --> 18:37.000
Okay,

18:37.400 --> 18:38.530
I'll learn from her.

18:39.480 --> 18:40.680
I made noodles today.

18:40.680 --> 18:42.210
Do you want to eat together?

18:47.160 --> 18:48.420
I'll eat in my own room.

18:51.960 --> 18:52.440
Mom!

18:53.510 --> 18:54.200
Good news.

18:54.540 --> 18:56.070
Our business license has been approved.

18:56.070 --> 18:56.660
Really?

18:57.000 --> 18:57.440
Look.

18:58.700 --> 18:59.670
This is great.

18:58.870 --> 19:00.810
[Individual Business License]

19:01.790 --> 19:02.590
It's just that

19:03.070 --> 19:04.870
I haven't worked for a long time.

19:05.550 --> 19:06.650
I'm worried I won't get used to it.

19:06.650 --> 19:07.550
I still need to adapt

19:07.550 --> 19:08.240
and learn.

19:09.380 --> 19:10.780
And once I start working,

19:11.000 --> 19:11.750
Granny Yu...

19:13.070 --> 19:14.670
Don't worry. Just go to work.

19:15.020 --> 19:15.990
I'm not so old that

19:15.990 --> 19:18.520
I need someone following me around
every day.

19:19.110 --> 19:21.070
Put some vinegar in my noodles.

19:21.640 --> 19:22.110
Got it.

19:24.830 --> 19:26.160
Hello, Manager Liu.

19:28.550 --> 19:29.030
Hello.

19:29.510 --> 19:30.350
Welcome.

19:32.530 --> 19:33.240
Morning, Boss.

19:32.930 --> 19:36.240
[Zhenzhu Building Materials Shop]

19:33.270 --> 19:33.870
Take care.

19:34.070 --> 19:34.870
Come by again.

19:37.400 --> 19:37.860
Junior.

19:38.310 --> 19:39.680
What was the bottom price

19:39.680 --> 19:41.350
that Mr. Zhou quoted us last time?

19:41.350 --> 19:42.750
If it's higher than our cost,

19:42.750 --> 19:43.680
let's go with it.

19:44.550 --> 19:46.160
But we'd hardly make any profit like this.

19:46.160 --> 19:48.310
We'll just have to learn from this loss.

19:48.310 --> 19:50.510
We've got to recover the losses
bit by bit.

19:50.510 --> 19:51.550
Sis Bai.

19:52.000 --> 19:53.240
You're here, Wei.

19:54.350 --> 19:55.270
Busy?

19:55.960 --> 19:56.960
Yes.

19:58.350 --> 19:59.550
I have some good news.

19:59.920 --> 20:00.780
Want to hear it?

20:01.320 --> 20:02.520
What good news?

20:02.550 --> 20:03.810
Acting so mysterious.

20:04.580 --> 20:05.960
I don't take on anything
that doesn't turn a profit.

20:05.960 --> 20:07.640
If I end up losing money,
I'll send you back to Jingcheng.

20:07.640 --> 20:09.370
You'll definitely make money.

20:10.270 --> 20:12.160
And I'm talking big money.

20:13.240 --> 20:13.840
Come here.

20:13.960 --> 20:14.640
Let me tell you.

20:14.640 --> 20:15.440
Hurry, hurry.

20:17.720 --> 20:18.400
Come on.

20:18.920 --> 20:19.720
Bring it out.

20:21.590 --> 20:22.320
Check it out.

20:23.110 --> 20:24.510
Good for you!

20:24.970 --> 20:26.000
Transistor radios

20:26.000 --> 20:27.260
are really trendy now.

20:27.270 --> 20:28.400
Where did you get it?

20:29.000 --> 20:29.860
Let me tell you.

20:29.920 --> 20:31.320
These all came from the factory's

20:31.320 --> 20:32.640
quality control rejects.

20:32.640 --> 20:34.350
But you know what?
After replacing the parts,

20:34.350 --> 20:35.550
they work perfectly.

20:35.750 --> 20:37.070
If you're still unsure,

20:37.070 --> 20:38.480
we can test a few more.

20:39.350 --> 20:40.350
It's 90 yuan each,

20:40.750 --> 20:42.610
and there are 500 pieces in total.

20:43.040 --> 20:44.770
I can't handle them all myself.

20:48.330 --> 20:49.400
Xia Xiaolan's clothing store

20:49.400 --> 20:50.730
is opening soon, right?

20:50.830 --> 20:52.320
Remember to send a flower basket.

20:52.320 --> 20:52.670
No.

20:53.000 --> 20:53.720
Send 10.

20:54.000 --> 20:55.550
Arrange for 10 people to deliver them.

20:55.550 --> 20:56.550
Make sure to fill the whole street.

20:56.550 --> 20:57.350
Young Master.

20:58.160 --> 21:01.350
She just rented that shop.

21:02.660 --> 21:03.640
The renovation will take

21:03.640 --> 21:04.550
some time.

21:05.440 --> 21:07.440
Then... I'll treat her to dinner.

21:07.960 --> 21:10.220
To congratulate her on renting the shop.

21:10.550 --> 21:11.210
Okay, okay.

21:12.400 --> 21:13.590
That...

21:13.960 --> 21:15.640
That boyfriend of hers—
what's his name again?

21:15.640 --> 21:17.440
It's Zhou... Zhou something.

21:17.750 --> 21:18.510
Zhou Cheng.

21:19.680 --> 21:22.410
That darn bastard in my way
should just drop dead.

21:22.920 --> 21:24.550
Should we get someone

21:24.750 --> 21:26.410
to make him drop dead for real?

21:26.590 --> 21:27.920
Do you think I'm stupid?

21:28.510 --> 21:29.970
If he really dropped dead,

21:30.510 --> 21:31.680
wouldn't Xia Xiaolan

21:31.680 --> 21:33.590
remember him for the rest of her life?

21:33.590 --> 21:35.320
You're so smart, Young Master.

21:35.680 --> 21:37.340
But later, when you have time,

21:37.720 --> 21:38.680
look into him.

21:39.070 --> 21:40.800
See what he's actually made of.

21:41.510 --> 21:42.000
Okay.

21:43.110 --> 21:44.830
We are in Shengcheng now,

21:45.030 --> 21:45.830
not Gangdao.

21:46.370 --> 21:47.150
Don't bring those ways

21:47.150 --> 21:48.070
here.

21:48.750 --> 21:50.440
Whether it's making money
or chasing women,

21:50.440 --> 21:51.640
my dad's ways

21:51.750 --> 21:53.010
are totally outdated.

21:53.030 --> 21:53.760
Understood.

21:56.000 --> 21:57.030
What's my dad

21:57.160 --> 21:58.020
up to recently?

21:58.200 --> 22:00.270
Master seems

22:00.270 --> 22:01.600
to be into art recently.

22:01.840 --> 22:03.440
He found a teacher in Gangdao

22:03.440 --> 22:05.100
to learn... What was it again?

22:05.480 --> 22:06.240
Tango.

22:08.550 --> 22:09.280
That's good.

22:09.590 --> 22:10.480
He should find something

22:10.480 --> 22:11.550
to keep himself busy.

22:11.550 --> 22:12.030
Right.

22:13.240 --> 22:14.040
Young Master.

22:14.440 --> 22:15.200
Young Master.

22:15.200 --> 22:16.400
It's Xia Dajun.

22:17.120 --> 22:17.720
Young Master!

22:17.720 --> 22:19.000
Xia Dajun?

22:19.240 --> 22:20.310
What does he want from me?

22:20.310 --> 22:20.830
No idea.

22:20.830 --> 22:22.630
I don't want to see him right now.

22:24.270 --> 22:25.790
Forget it. He saved my life once.

22:25.790 --> 22:26.480
Let him in.

22:26.510 --> 22:26.920
Okay.

22:32.350 --> 22:33.210
Please come in.

22:35.160 --> 22:35.590
Dajun.

22:35.850 --> 22:36.310
Young Master.

22:36.310 --> 22:37.160
What's the matter?

22:37.160 --> 22:37.960
Have a seat.

22:38.240 --> 22:38.920
No, thanks.

22:40.110 --> 22:41.970
My family has come to Shengcheng.

22:42.400 --> 22:43.240
Your family?

22:44.680 --> 22:45.550
My mother,

22:45.890 --> 22:47.020
my younger brother,

22:47.070 --> 22:47.830
his wife,

22:48.120 --> 22:48.760
and their kid...

22:48.760 --> 22:50.070
Alright, alright, I get it.

22:50.070 --> 22:51.270
Just get to the point.

22:53.280 --> 22:54.480
Here's the thing.

22:55.070 --> 22:56.800
They've been here for 2 months.

22:57.750 --> 22:59.010
We bought some things,

22:59.310 --> 23:01.040
and I'm running short on money.

23:01.710 --> 23:02.920
Young Master, do you think

23:02.920 --> 23:05.180
I could get an advance on next month's...

23:06.160 --> 23:07.350
Got it, got it.

23:07.920 --> 23:08.440
Hua.

23:08.680 --> 23:09.610
Go to accounting

23:09.640 --> 23:11.900
and advance two months' salary to Dajun.

23:12.270 --> 23:13.440
O-Okay.

23:13.750 --> 23:15.270
Thank you so much, Young Master.

23:15.270 --> 23:16.640
Thank you very much.

23:16.960 --> 23:17.890
You're welcome.

23:18.480 --> 23:19.200
But Dajun,

23:20.110 --> 23:21.480
you've been with me in Shengcheng

23:21.480 --> 23:22.740
for a while now, right?

23:24.160 --> 23:25.160
I see that

23:25.240 --> 23:26.270
your family is all here now,

23:26.270 --> 23:28.040
and your old injuries haven't healed.

23:28.040 --> 23:29.100
Why don't I arrange

23:29.110 --> 23:30.640
an office job for you?

23:32.270 --> 23:33.110
An office job?

23:36.510 --> 23:37.070
Young Master.

23:37.070 --> 23:38.720
I'd rather serve you by your side.

23:38.720 --> 23:40.740
Working in the office is still serving me.

23:40.740 --> 23:41.870
It's just that the hours

23:41.870 --> 23:42.880
will be more regular.

23:42.880 --> 23:43.620
It'll also be easier for you

23:43.620 --> 23:45.150
to take care of your family.

23:45.430 --> 23:45.910
Hua.

23:46.170 --> 23:47.030
Go to the office

23:47.060 --> 23:48.590
and arrange a suitable position

23:48.590 --> 23:49.440
for Dajun.

23:50.070 --> 23:51.400
You'll start next week.

23:53.270 --> 23:54.580
I'll be going now.

23:55.640 --> 23:56.170
Goodbye.

23:56.880 --> 23:57.400
Go on.

23:58.590 --> 23:59.200
Dajun.

23:59.770 --> 24:00.850
Office work offers

24:00.880 --> 24:02.000
promotions and raises.

24:02.000 --> 24:02.600
Work hard.

24:04.550 --> 24:05.110
Goodbye.

24:11.160 --> 24:11.960
Young Master.

24:12.600 --> 24:14.180
Xia Dajun can't even read.

24:14.240 --> 24:15.900
Why let him work in the office?

24:16.030 --> 24:17.070
You don't even know

24:17.070 --> 24:17.830
how to arrange a position?

24:17.830 --> 24:20.360
Seems like you've lost your place
serving me.

24:20.990 --> 24:22.720
Then is cleaning toilets okay?

24:29.830 --> 24:30.340
Li.

24:31.160 --> 24:32.160
Where's Zhenzhu?

24:33.040 --> 24:34.880
Senior went with Kang Wei to get stock.

24:34.880 --> 24:36.270
She asked you guys to go ahead,

24:36.270 --> 24:37.320
and they'll be there in a bit.

24:37.320 --> 24:38.350
It's getting dark.

24:38.350 --> 24:39.950
What stock are they getting?

24:40.030 --> 24:41.960
Kang Wei came over this afternoon.

24:42.080 --> 24:43.790
They chatted inside for a while,

24:43.790 --> 24:44.500
made a couple of calls,

24:44.500 --> 24:45.830
and then left together.

24:46.110 --> 24:47.910
I think they went to the seaside.

25:04.070 --> 25:05.070
Oh no. This is bad.

25:06.790 --> 25:07.200
Li.

25:07.410 --> 25:08.200
By 8 PM tonight,

25:08.200 --> 25:09.440
if we haven't returned,

25:09.440 --> 25:09.830
call the police.

25:09.830 --> 25:10.160
Okay.

25:11.480 --> 25:12.410
Call the police?

25:17.550 --> 25:18.590
You don't think those two

25:18.590 --> 25:20.380
are actually smuggling goods, do you?

25:20.380 --> 25:22.160
They wouldn't have the guts, right?

25:22.160 --> 25:22.750
Our law firm recently

25:22.750 --> 25:24.110
took on a smuggling case.

25:24.110 --> 25:25.070
The files say

25:25.140 --> 25:25.790
there's still a large batch

25:25.790 --> 25:27.450
of small appliances missing.

25:28.270 --> 25:29.850
There are too many containers here.

25:29.850 --> 25:30.640
Checking them one by one

25:30.640 --> 25:31.770
would take too long.

25:36.110 --> 25:37.240
Let's go over there.

25:45.640 --> 25:47.000
It's too dangerous here.

25:47.000 --> 25:47.800
You stay here.

25:47.960 --> 25:49.030
I'll go meet up with the police then.

25:49.030 --> 25:49.920
You stall them.

25:50.000 --> 25:50.400
Okay.

25:50.550 --> 25:51.210
Be careful.

25:58.620 --> 25:59.300
Mr. Qiao.

25:59.480 --> 26:01.080
Let's skip the pleasantries

26:01.110 --> 26:02.770
and get straight to the goods.

26:17.540 --> 26:18.880
We need to check the goods first.

26:18.880 --> 26:20.210
You can check the goods,

26:21.270 --> 26:22.030
but

26:22.440 --> 26:23.900
we have to do it elsewhere.

26:26.790 --> 26:27.520
Don't worry.

26:28.210 --> 26:29.920
For the amount of goods you want

26:29.920 --> 26:31.380
and the money you brought,

26:32.110 --> 26:34.440
I wouldn't kill you for it.

26:34.920 --> 26:35.440
Right?

26:35.920 --> 26:36.480
Mr. Qiao,

26:36.680 --> 26:38.080
that's not what we meant.

26:38.270 --> 26:39.480
Since Jian introduced you to me,

26:39.480 --> 26:40.680
of course I trust you.

26:40.830 --> 26:42.000
But we're paying

26:42.030 --> 26:42.790
real money

26:42.790 --> 26:44.000
for tens of thousands worth of goods,

26:44.000 --> 26:45.270
so we have to check.

26:45.510 --> 26:47.570
-Then we'll feel more assu...
-Kang!

26:51.030 --> 26:51.880
You really have the guts

26:51.880 --> 26:53.810
to do business behind my back, huh?

26:55.160 --> 26:56.640
What's this supposed to mean?

26:56.640 --> 26:57.970
I'm here to do business.

27:03.830 --> 27:04.640
Big business.

27:08.270 --> 27:09.930
I really am here for business.

27:17.440 --> 27:18.240
What,

27:18.960 --> 27:19.850
did you two really think

27:19.850 --> 27:20.270
you could call the shots

27:20.270 --> 27:21.350
on this deal?

27:21.960 --> 27:23.550
If Li hadn't tipped me off,

27:24.440 --> 27:25.510
I wouldn't have caught you two

27:25.510 --> 27:27.970
embezzling merchandise funds red-handed.

27:28.070 --> 27:28.930
Who is this guy?

27:31.400 --> 27:32.190
Who am I?

27:33.270 --> 27:34.130
Let me tell you—

27:35.160 --> 27:36.240
I'm the real boss.

27:36.920 --> 27:38.320
Why do business with them

27:39.070 --> 27:40.470
when you can do it with me?

27:40.510 --> 27:41.790
Whatever they're paying,

27:41.790 --> 27:42.790
I'll pay double.

27:44.200 --> 27:45.000
But

27:46.110 --> 27:46.960
tell these two

27:47.400 --> 27:49.400
to get the hell out of here right now!

27:49.980 --> 27:51.160
I'm absolutely not doing business

27:51.160 --> 27:52.370
with these backstabbing bastards

27:52.370 --> 27:53.610
anymore.

28:00.680 --> 28:02.410
Who's leaving is yet to be seen.

28:02.640 --> 28:04.110
You think you're so tough

28:04.110 --> 28:05.360
with your stinking money?

28:05.360 --> 28:06.440
Let's see if you can pull off this deal

28:06.440 --> 28:07.270
without me.

28:07.460 --> 28:07.920
Mr. Qiao,

28:07.920 --> 28:09.320
make them leave first...

28:42.360 --> 28:42.920
Stop!

28:43.390 --> 28:44.220
Stop! Stop!

28:46.110 --> 28:46.880
Here! Here!

28:46.880 --> 28:47.510
Officers!

28:53.310 --> 28:54.750
The fact that you called the police

28:54.750 --> 28:55.680
shows you've got

28:55.680 --> 28:56.680
some legal awareness.

28:56.680 --> 28:57.200
But

28:57.790 --> 28:58.480
don't get overconfident

28:58.480 --> 29:00.350
just because
you know some fighting skills.

29:00.350 --> 29:01.160
These people

29:01.470 --> 29:02.470
are armed

29:02.830 --> 29:03.750
and very dangerous—

29:03.750 --> 29:04.750
not something a few youngsters like you

29:04.750 --> 29:05.410
can handle.

29:06.200 --> 29:06.750
We have also been

29:06.750 --> 29:08.350
cracking down on this group.

29:08.400 --> 29:09.830
If anything like this happens
in the future,

29:09.830 --> 29:11.220
call the police immediately

29:11.220 --> 29:12.130
and wait for us to handle it.

29:12.130 --> 29:12.680
Understood?

29:12.680 --> 29:13.200
Understood.

29:13.200 --> 29:13.790
Understood.

29:13.790 --> 29:14.440
You guys,

29:14.640 --> 29:15.640
come back to the station with me

29:15.640 --> 29:17.000
and explain the situation.

29:17.000 --> 29:17.350
Okay.

29:19.880 --> 29:20.740
Take them away.

29:21.110 --> 29:21.480
Move!

29:22.110 --> 29:22.440
Move!

29:22.750 --> 29:23.720
Follow up! Follow up!

29:23.720 --> 29:24.240
Move!

29:24.350 --> 29:24.830
Follow up!

29:24.830 --> 29:25.270
Move!

29:25.480 --> 29:26.830
What's this?

29:27.410 --> 29:28.410
It's the new

29:28.440 --> 29:30.240
24-inch color TV he bought.

29:30.480 --> 29:31.790
It's huge!

29:31.880 --> 29:33.960
Can we turn it on and have a look?

29:36.750 --> 29:37.310
Mom.

29:38.030 --> 29:38.680
Mom!

29:39.070 --> 29:39.680
Mom!

29:41.240 --> 29:41.750
Mom!

29:42.480 --> 29:43.490
What are you doing?

29:43.490 --> 29:45.240
Why are you taking a quilt
into the kitchen?

29:45.240 --> 29:46.270
I don't want to sleep with Junshan

29:46.270 --> 29:47.270
and Junbao anymore.

29:47.270 --> 29:47.720
They're too noisy.

29:47.720 --> 29:48.240
I don't want to sleep

29:48.240 --> 29:49.400
with her either.

29:50.000 --> 29:51.130
Shut up, both of you!

29:51.270 --> 29:51.880
Stop it!

29:54.750 --> 29:56.370
Where do you want to sleep
if not with them?

29:56.370 --> 29:57.370
This room is tiny.

29:57.830 --> 29:59.490
Sleep on the floor if you want.

30:00.040 --> 30:01.320
I'll sleep here!

30:01.350 --> 30:01.810
I'll...

30:03.310 --> 30:03.920
Sorry, Grandma.

30:03.920 --> 30:04.440
Oh my.

30:05.440 --> 30:07.310
What a waste of my wine.

30:08.700 --> 30:10.270
Sleep wherever you want.

30:10.480 --> 30:12.030
Just don't eye my room.

30:14.970 --> 30:16.500
What are you staring at

30:16.520 --> 30:17.920
with your eyes wide open?

30:18.270 --> 30:20.680
If you don't like it, go get a job.

30:21.830 --> 30:24.130
They cover room and board,

30:24.160 --> 30:25.560
and you'll earn a salary.

30:31.680 --> 30:32.140
Mother.

30:33.110 --> 30:34.240
Dajun, you're back.

30:34.350 --> 30:35.080
Uncle Dajun.

30:35.960 --> 30:36.750
Well,

30:37.510 --> 30:38.270
Jingui.

30:39.170 --> 30:40.300
Dajun, you're here.

30:40.790 --> 30:42.000
Take these inside.

30:42.440 --> 30:42.880
Dajun,

30:43.110 --> 30:43.770
have a seat.

30:45.250 --> 30:45.930
Dajun,

30:46.680 --> 30:47.350
aren't you working at

30:47.350 --> 30:49.650
that com...

30:49.680 --> 30:50.610
That com-com...

30:50.720 --> 30:51.920
It's company, Grandma.

30:51.920 --> 30:52.850
What "com-com"?

30:53.750 --> 30:55.400
Right. Yes, company.

30:55.730 --> 30:57.210
Aren't you working at

30:57.240 --> 30:58.180
a big company—

30:58.200 --> 30:59.680
living in a big house,

30:59.680 --> 31:00.740
eating fancy meals,

31:00.740 --> 31:02.070
and drinking fine wine?

31:02.270 --> 31:03.290
So you still remember that

31:03.290 --> 31:04.880
I'm living in this cramped hole?

31:04.880 --> 31:05.440
Mother.

31:05.750 --> 31:07.400
I live in the company dorm.

31:07.680 --> 31:08.740
It's just one room.

31:09.640 --> 31:11.160
Rent in the city isn't cheap.

31:11.160 --> 31:12.920
I can't afford anything bigger.

31:12.920 --> 31:13.850
Can't afford it?

31:15.030 --> 31:16.720
So you're just telling me

31:16.720 --> 31:18.120
you have no money, right?

31:18.480 --> 31:19.940
Who are you trying to fool?

31:19.980 --> 31:21.960
You think just because I don't go out,

31:21.960 --> 31:23.220
I don't know anything?

31:23.520 --> 31:24.440
Your boss pays you

31:24.440 --> 31:25.440
hundreds a month.

31:25.440 --> 31:26.590
I know it perfectly well.

31:26.590 --> 31:27.830
How dare you lie to me?

31:28.880 --> 31:30.830
There are so many mouths to feed,

31:31.900 --> 31:33.750
plus rent, groceries,

31:33.880 --> 31:35.960
and water and electricity bills...

31:37.790 --> 31:38.750
So you're reluctant

31:38.750 --> 31:40.280
to buy things for me, right?

31:41.170 --> 31:42.200
If you're reluctant, don't buy anything.

31:42.200 --> 31:43.750
How could I be reluctant?

31:45.880 --> 31:46.310
Dajun.

31:47.070 --> 31:47.750
Have some warm water.

31:47.750 --> 31:49.640
Hongbing isn't back yet?

31:51.030 --> 31:51.880
Well...

31:52.150 --> 31:52.830
You know...

31:53.030 --> 31:54.560
He went out to look for a job.

31:54.690 --> 31:55.590
It's quite easy to find a job

31:55.590 --> 31:56.830
here, you know?

31:57.350 --> 31:58.750
But there's a problem.

31:58.880 --> 31:59.550
The thing is,

31:59.550 --> 32:00.960
either the pay is too low

32:01.160 --> 32:02.510
or the work is too tiring.

32:02.510 --> 32:03.350
Back in the village,

32:03.350 --> 32:03.940
he injured his back

32:03.940 --> 32:05.340
while working, you know?

32:05.590 --> 32:07.250
So he can't do heavy labor now.

32:07.550 --> 32:08.200
Jingui.

32:09.070 --> 32:10.720
About this matter,

32:11.000 --> 32:12.070
for our Dajun,

32:12.070 --> 32:13.200
it's nothing at all.

32:14.160 --> 32:16.680
As the old saying goes,

32:17.160 --> 32:21.160
"once a man hits it big,
his whole family benefits."

32:21.770 --> 32:22.610
Our Dajun

32:22.640 --> 32:24.170
once saved his boss's life.

32:24.290 --> 32:25.520
That makes our whole family

32:25.520 --> 32:27.320
his boss's benefactors, right?

32:28.030 --> 32:28.830
Right, right.

32:29.270 --> 32:30.610
I forgot about that.

32:30.640 --> 32:31.440
Well,

32:31.590 --> 32:33.350
go back and tell your boss

32:33.750 --> 32:35.880
that I said

32:36.790 --> 32:38.050
to give our Hongbing

32:38.240 --> 32:39.790
a job by his side.

32:40.590 --> 32:41.560
He's not in good health,

32:41.560 --> 32:42.520
so no heavy work.

32:42.550 --> 32:43.160
Right, right.

32:43.160 --> 32:44.440
He can't do heavy labor.

32:44.440 --> 32:46.200
Why turn down easy money, right?

32:46.200 --> 32:47.600
Why shouldn't we earn it?

32:48.200 --> 32:49.730
Even a little money is fine.

32:51.610 --> 32:52.130
Mother.

32:52.680 --> 32:54.590
I borrowed this from my boss.

32:54.960 --> 32:56.560
My boss assigned me a new job,

32:56.960 --> 32:59.270
so I'll have more time

32:59.270 --> 33:00.930
to take care of you from now on.

33:02.070 --> 33:03.880
That's the way!

33:04.080 --> 33:05.480
Earn more money in the future,

33:05.480 --> 33:06.810
and bring me more money.

33:06.880 --> 33:09.810
That's the best way to show
your filial respect to me.

33:11.390 --> 33:12.350
Mother, take your time eating.

33:12.350 --> 33:13.280
I'm leaving now.

33:14.380 --> 33:15.030
Dajun!

33:15.200 --> 33:16.930
About Hongbing's work,

33:16.960 --> 33:18.270
don't forget about it!

33:18.530 --> 33:19.370
You... You...

33:19.400 --> 33:20.960
Look at you, so clueless.

33:20.960 --> 33:23.020
Hurry up and see your Uncle Dajun out.

33:23.670 --> 33:25.030
Why are you still standing there?

33:25.030 --> 33:26.070
-Uncle Dajun!
-Seriously.

33:26.070 --> 33:27.130
Let me walk you out!

33:37.510 --> 33:37.960
Well,

33:37.960 --> 33:39.490
don't look so down, you all.

33:39.720 --> 33:40.130
Look,

33:40.160 --> 33:40.790
we've been through

33:40.790 --> 33:42.390
life and death together now.

33:44.790 --> 33:45.450
Stop there!

33:46.070 --> 33:46.550
Sis Bai!

33:46.550 --> 33:47.880
Bro, stop chasing! Stop!

33:47.880 --> 33:48.610
Are you okay?

33:48.750 --> 33:49.480
Are you okay?

33:50.480 --> 33:51.030
Who are you?

33:51.030 --> 33:51.760
I surrender.

33:52.350 --> 33:53.070
I stole something.

33:53.070 --> 33:53.750
Speak properly.

33:53.750 --> 33:55.280
This is the police station.

33:56.750 --> 33:57.310
Comrade.

33:57.720 --> 33:58.720
Are you all right?

33:59.440 --> 34:00.440
Let me take a look.

34:01.200 --> 34:02.530
Hey, what are you doing?

34:02.680 --> 34:03.030
I...

34:06.720 --> 34:07.690
It was dislocated.

34:07.690 --> 34:08.670
I just set it back in place for you.

34:08.670 --> 34:09.469
Try moving it.

34:15.350 --> 34:16.679
You'd better go to the hospital
for an X-ray.

34:16.679 --> 34:17.449
to rule out

34:17.480 --> 34:18.880
any further bone issues.

34:23.440 --> 34:25.100
Th-Thanks.

34:26.590 --> 34:26.960
Officer.

34:26.960 --> 34:27.440
Are you okay?

34:27.440 --> 34:28.170
He's a thief.

34:28.280 --> 34:29.400
I saw him stealing.

34:29.760 --> 34:30.560
I'm a witness.

34:30.760 --> 34:31.510
I'm the thief.

34:31.510 --> 34:32.630
What happened to your face?

34:32.630 --> 34:34.290
I... I fell and hurt it myself.

34:34.320 --> 34:35.520
You two, come with me.

34:35.960 --> 34:36.360
Okay.

34:43.909 --> 34:44.960
Alright, let's go.

34:44.960 --> 34:45.400
Go on.

34:46.050 --> 34:46.630
Let's go.

34:50.840 --> 34:51.440
Sis Bai.

34:52.230 --> 34:52.920
Sis Bai?

34:53.760 --> 34:57.220
What are you doing? Waiting for
another thief to bump into you?

35:15.150 --> 35:16.590
Sis Bai has the best fighting skills,

35:16.590 --> 35:18.450
yet Sis Bai is the one who got hurt.

35:22.820 --> 35:23.760
Didn't you say there'd be

35:23.760 --> 35:25.890
absolutely no issues with this batch?

35:26.590 --> 35:28.050
You call this "no issues"?

35:29.000 --> 35:30.400
If Zhou Cheng hadn't

35:30.430 --> 35:32.230
brought the police there today,

35:32.470 --> 35:34.230
either these goods would be confiscated

35:34.230 --> 35:35.510
and our hard-earned money

35:35.510 --> 35:36.840
would go down the drain,

35:37.050 --> 35:38.150
or we'd have to sell them secretly,

35:38.150 --> 35:39.000
basically becoming accomplices

35:39.000 --> 35:41.190
to smugglers in selling smuggled goods!

35:41.190 --> 35:42.760
If your business fails,

35:42.840 --> 35:44.070
you can go back to Jingcheng.

35:44.070 --> 35:44.920
But what about me?

35:44.920 --> 35:46.450
Did you ever think about me?

35:47.110 --> 35:48.760
You almost ruined me!

35:52.840 --> 35:53.320
Sis Bai.

35:54.400 --> 35:56.130
Wei was also scammed, you know.

35:58.440 --> 35:59.000
Wei.

35:59.710 --> 36:01.910
You can't blame Sis Bai for being angry.

36:02.190 --> 36:03.790
It's one thing to lose money;

36:03.920 --> 36:06.180
but today, you put your safety in danger.

36:08.030 --> 36:09.090
So what should I do?

36:10.550 --> 36:12.150
Then tell me what I should do!

36:12.830 --> 36:13.720
Don't you think I feel bad

36:13.720 --> 36:14.580
that things turned out like this?

36:14.580 --> 36:15.470
Did I want this?

36:16.960 --> 36:18.490
I've been in Shengcheng for a month,

36:18.490 --> 36:19.360
running around like a headless chicken

36:19.360 --> 36:20.940
without accomplishing anything!

36:20.940 --> 36:21.500
My uncle

36:21.760 --> 36:22.970
came all the way here a few days ago

36:22.970 --> 36:23.630
and scolded me!

36:23.630 --> 36:25.030
He wanted me to go back with him,

36:25.030 --> 36:25.920
but I refused!

36:26.230 --> 36:26.960
I just wanted to prove

36:26.960 --> 36:28.360
that my choice was right!

36:51.440 --> 36:53.040
Wei just came to Shengcheng.

36:53.410 --> 36:54.480
He really didn't know

36:54.480 --> 36:55.960
how complicated things are here.

36:55.960 --> 36:56.920
But you're different.

36:56.920 --> 36:58.520
How could you be so careless?

37:00.010 --> 37:00.850
I know

37:00.870 --> 37:02.800
this wasn't entirely Wei's fault.

37:02.800 --> 37:04.000
My shop just opened,

37:04.320 --> 37:05.850
business hasn't picked up,

37:05.960 --> 37:07.510
and we lost money recently.

37:08.030 --> 37:09.030
So I got anxious.

37:10.590 --> 37:11.990
Why didn't you come to me?

37:12.150 --> 37:12.710
We all

37:12.800 --> 37:14.200
have own own things to do,

37:14.510 --> 37:15.710
and we all need money.

37:15.960 --> 37:16.710
I thought

37:17.290 --> 37:18.150
if I could solve it myself,

37:18.150 --> 37:19.480
I shouldn't bother you.

37:48.920 --> 37:49.450
Alright.

37:49.880 --> 37:50.740
That's enough.

37:53.920 --> 37:54.480
Sis Bai.

37:55.710 --> 37:56.320
I failed

37:56.320 --> 37:57.230
your trust.

37:58.920 --> 37:59.920
The money we lost—

38:00.030 --> 38:01.690
I'll definitely earn it back.

38:02.030 --> 38:03.360
I'll do it the right way—

38:03.670 --> 38:05.000
honestly and steadily.

38:08.110 --> 38:09.710
The first step is always the hardest,

38:09.710 --> 38:11.150
but it won't always be like this.

38:11.150 --> 38:13.230
Miracles happen every day in Shengcheng.

38:13.230 --> 38:14.320
Why can't it be us?

38:14.710 --> 38:15.110
Right.

38:15.590 --> 38:16.650
I just want to prove

38:16.800 --> 38:17.930
that the path I chose

38:18.190 --> 38:19.120
is the right one.

38:19.480 --> 38:20.340
Kang Lianming!

38:20.350 --> 38:28.320
♪ The stars flow across the sky,
and I walk this road with you ♪

38:21.800 --> 38:23.630
You can't look down on me!

38:26.570 --> 38:28.190
If you eat salted fish,
you must bear the thirst.

38:28.190 --> 38:29.840
Endure the hard times,
and good days will come.

38:29.130 --> 38:33.070
♪ From strangers,
our hearts slowly grow close ♪

38:31.190 --> 38:32.320
What's that you're saying?

38:32.320 --> 38:33.210
I believe in you.

38:33.210 --> 38:36.590
♪ Quietly, we treat each other
with sincerity ♪

38:34.360 --> 38:36.290
We'll definitely live a good life.

38:37.030 --> 38:37.490
Come on!

38:37.560 --> 38:45.480
♪ Life is like a dream,
and friends are like a mist ♪

38:38.440 --> 38:39.320
We must knock all those

38:39.320 --> 38:40.400
who look down on us

38:40.630 --> 38:41.400
down!

38:41.590 --> 38:42.440
Knock them down!

38:42.440 --> 38:42.840
Right!

38:43.190 --> 38:44.960
Don't look down on the poor youth!

38:44.960 --> 38:46.550
We're not really poor, though.

38:46.550 --> 38:46.960
Right.

38:46.640 --> 38:50.420
♪ True confidants are rare,
after storms and trials ♪

38:47.320 --> 38:48.230
You know what I mean.

38:48.230 --> 38:50.640
Alright then.
Don't look down on the poor youth,

38:50.640 --> 38:57.540
♪ The one who never steps back for me,
that is you ♪

38:50.920 --> 38:53.380
don't look down on
the inexperienced youth,

38:53.400 --> 38:55.760
and don't look down on the youth
whose ambitions are yet unfulfilled!

38:55.760 --> 38:58.480
Don't look down on the youth
whose ambitions are yet unfulfilled!

38:58.280 --> 39:02.210
♪ In the distant night sky,
the scattered stars are all connected ♪

39:02.240 --> 39:07.740
♪ Even if the road ahead
is full of thorns ♪

39:08.580 --> 39:11.710
♪ You help untangle
the loneliness in my heart ♪

39:11.740 --> 39:15.300
♪ Who truly understands me? ♪

39:15.640 --> 39:16.480
Watching my lover

39:15.700 --> 39:19.610
♪ Like two hands,
together in joy and in sorrow ♪

39:16.760 --> 39:17.820
and my good friends

39:18.030 --> 39:19.030
argue together,

39:19.070 --> 39:19.800
mess around together,

39:19.640 --> 39:25.320
♪ We share everything,
never dividing between you and me ♪

39:20.110 --> 39:22.570
and want to take on the whole world
together—

39:22.630 --> 39:23.960
I wouldn't have even dared to imagine

39:23.960 --> 39:25.490
such a passionate,
almost cringey kind of scene

39:25.490 --> 39:27.550
in my past life.

39:26.110 --> 39:30.250
♪ You for me, and I for you ♪

39:31.060 --> 39:37.210
♪ Facing hardship and despair together,
tightly holding your hand ♪

39:38.070 --> 39:42.260
♪ My friend ♪

39:53.110 --> 39:55.440
Those two must have been terrified today.

39:55.800 --> 39:57.530
You were terrified too, right?

40:21.670 --> 40:23.270
What are you thinking about?

40:26.070 --> 40:27.190
I was wondering

40:28.400 --> 40:29.480
if I made starting a business

40:29.480 --> 40:30.510
seem too simple.

40:32.320 --> 40:33.580
I thought having ideas

40:34.000 --> 40:34.840
and courage

40:35.440 --> 40:36.900
was enough to forge ahead.

40:38.110 --> 40:39.280
But I forgot

40:40.630 --> 40:43.290
that while this place
is full of opportunities,

40:43.400 --> 40:45.030
it's also full of traps.

40:46.800 --> 40:48.150
Was it because I seemed too confident

40:48.150 --> 40:49.190
about everything

40:50.070 --> 40:52.400
that I made everyone let their guard down?

41:00.770 --> 41:01.670
You're not some kind of

41:01.670 --> 41:03.200
all-knowing god after all.

41:04.000 --> 41:05.280
When young people start a business,

41:05.280 --> 41:07.480
who hasn't gone through
their share of hardships?

41:07.480 --> 41:08.080
Look at us—

41:08.840 --> 41:10.040
being here together,

41:10.400 --> 41:11.860
working hard side by side—

41:12.400 --> 41:13.860
isn't that the best thing?

41:17.190 --> 41:17.670
Yes.

41:19.960 --> 41:21.220
Though Wei and Zhenzhu

41:21.360 --> 41:22.560
were a bit impulsive,

41:23.120 --> 41:23.840
it also proves

41:23.840 --> 41:25.500
that they still have courage.

41:25.890 --> 41:27.080
In the day-to-day

41:27.110 --> 41:28.710
hustle for life,

41:29.450 --> 41:30.850
the easiest thing to lose

41:30.960 --> 41:31.840
is courage.

41:36.440 --> 41:37.510
I have a friend.

41:39.710 --> 41:41.400
Since her family was poor,

41:42.240 --> 41:44.040
she's always relied on herself.

41:45.150 --> 41:47.210
From university into the workforce,

41:47.510 --> 41:49.570
she's cherished every opportunity,

41:53.960 --> 41:55.190
working hard

41:55.800 --> 41:57.330
while treading carefully.

41:57.960 --> 41:59.630
She was afraid of making mistakes,

41:59.630 --> 42:01.230
afraid of offending people,

42:01.450 --> 42:03.910
afraid that the hard-earned opportunities

42:03.920 --> 42:04.760
she's finally gotten

42:04.760 --> 42:06.220
might suddenly slip away.

42:07.880 --> 42:09.150
And yet, even so,

42:09.880 --> 42:11.740
she still hasn't gained respect,

42:12.360 --> 42:13.290
and things still

42:14.360 --> 42:16.090
haven't gone smoothly for her.

42:17.230 --> 42:18.630
But that's not her fault.

42:19.480 --> 42:21.280
No one knows right from the start

42:22.030 --> 42:23.490
which path to take in life.

42:24.280 --> 42:25.480
We all take detours.

42:27.920 --> 42:28.920
But

42:30.110 --> 42:31.170
we've got friends,

42:32.030 --> 42:32.750
family,

42:38.400 --> 42:39.260
and loved ones,

42:41.320 --> 42:42.650
so we won't lose our way.

42:47.840 --> 42:48.440
I know.

42:52.940 --> 42:54.400
Although we make mistakes

42:54.920 --> 42:56.250
and face difficulties,

42:56.920 --> 42:58.000
we must never

42:58.030 --> 42:59.070
lose our edge.

43:00.320 --> 43:00.980
Zhou Cheng,

43:01.800 --> 43:03.000
the same goes for you.

43:03.230 --> 43:04.840
If there's something you want to do,

43:04.840 --> 43:05.570
just go for it

43:06.280 --> 43:07.210
and fight for it.

43:08.030 --> 43:09.110
We may be young,

43:10.030 --> 43:10.920
but we're just as capable.
